<HEADLINE>
FT  19 DEC 92 / UK Company News: Turkey Trust little changed
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Net asset value per share of the Turkey Trust amounted to 148.06p at October
31, compared with 155.12p six months earlier and 148.97p at the previous
year-end.
After-tax revenue for the 12 months to end-October was little changed at
Pounds 601,000 (Pounds 605,000), equal to earnings of 6.13p (6.19p).
The dividend for the year is maintained at 5p, made up as to a same-again 4p
special and a 1p ordinary payment.
